<subSubSection id="284ADD1DC71AFF8EB968B9FE2C84FC11" pageId="null" pageNumber="134" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="508D275CE127095D0C1CB51694BBC337" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Aufrechte Betonie</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="ED2CF95496A66FF18CE7EC2B7EDAC1F4" pageId="null" pageNumber="134" type="description">
<paragraph id="51FC2BD1014CF0068BFD2F2F288C0211" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">
20-50 cm hoch. Stengel meist dicht behaart (Haare am obern Stengelteil 0,4-1,5 mm lang). 
<normalizedToken id="1F6EB94302423C0E5C94F83A0889F0DE" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
beiderseits meist zerstreut behaart. 
<normalizedToken id="E81570D649C1770CEE76E0AB9791BA6B" originalValue="Stengelblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Stengelblaetter</normalizedToken>
am Grunde 
<normalizedToken id="0DAC798349D9FAD9C18C7CA56553BB4E" originalValue="herzförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">herzfoermig</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken id="B4512F890C2B000E129B2B89F2939034" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
kompakt. 
<emphasis id="15D210E85F7E9210FFCEFA0DDB2122DF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Kelch 8</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="123B9FBDB77C55D2EAC9C908D393B45C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">11 mm lang, mit 2,3</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="96155BAF65FE0E5D8D578A2FDFBC4C84" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">
4,5 mm langen, 
<normalizedToken id="51F935BA8AB076430CFE8A43F055271C" originalValue="allmählich" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">allmaehlich</normalizedToken>
in die Granne sich 
<normalizedToken id="4A5F2C0F3303F96DD8F56E74C762AF1B" originalValue="verschmälernden" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">verschmaelernden</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="F9DB0DDEA99B16F94562C0F89C355901" originalValue="Zähnen" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Zaehnen</normalizedToken>
, im untern Teil kahl.
</emphasis>
Krone 12-16 mm lang. - 
<normalizedToken id="1B2DC12DE1CDB71CA5C8A72479273531" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B3CEC72840C88D37200AA170B65C63BA" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">
<emphasis id="A2E42578C37CB294907D04464633AB16" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CBCB4DA0A56E02789EE12E88C13E53AB" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">
<emphasis id="EE96156239F164809338611840CA1231" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Standort.</emphasis>
Montan und subalpin. 
<normalizedToken id="643955A89E811E7C90D980E520723B41" originalValue="Mäßig" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Maessig</normalizedToken>
trockene, kalkarme 
<normalizedToken id="3F404F834A417B369D38FB37B02FB29D" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Boeden</normalizedToken>
. Wiesen und 
<normalizedToken id="C542892C43C78FDA3F3D7A47B9E00912" originalValue="Gebüsche" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Gebuesche</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D0776F1FF3BDADF09326165F7E5603FB" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">
<emphasis id="6C1CA7BD200E1C1666453600773B59B5" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Verbreitung.</emphasis>
Nicht genau bekannt. - Im Gebiet: Vogesen, Alpen (Verbreitung ist festzustellen!).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E98DB20E989003FD4D235DDABC74C69E" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">
<emphasis id="BF451A8A83742039ADD3C79064D8BE6B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
Die 
<normalizedToken id="BE274B0904EA9902677FB48B9B52E5EA" originalValue="Identität" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Identitaet</normalizedToken>
unserer Pflanzen mit 
<taxonomicName id="8CB9BD3D32BBAAF0177018656AD03180" authority="Ait." authorityName="Ait." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Lamiaceae" genus="Betonica" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="134" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="stricta">
<emphasis id="E348215AE1C92739FB2D64A27486FCFA" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">B. stricta</emphasis>
Ait.
</taxonomicName>
ist umstritten.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
